      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a great little project to tinker with. It has the usual wear you\u2019d expect at this stage, but it still offers real value without the big price tag. If you want something cheap, approachable, and worth a look, this could be a great fit.",
