      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Budget-friendly project with strong bones and plenty of upside. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still offers a willing powertrain, solid chassis feel, and the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it appealing for a hands-on owner. Starts, moves, and delivers usable performance, with good candidate potential for a commuter, winter beater, or restoration-minded build. If you know how to turn a wrench and want something affordable with character, this one has real value.",
